                     <div class=\"tbasic\">\n                                <div class=\"tname\">王迎新</div>\n                                <div class=\"tposition\">副研究员 </div>\n                                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"tcontent\">\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>博士</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>电  话: 010-62781983</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>邮  箱: wangyingxin@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                   <p></p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                        </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu\">  \n                     \n       <li class=\"on\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教育背景</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">工作经历</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教学工作</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究领域</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究概况</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术成果</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术兼职</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">奖励荣誉</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n    </ul> \n    \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-on\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei;\">● </span></span>2004.09-2009.07</span>　<span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">清华大学工程物理系　获核科学与技术专业工学博士学位</span> <span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><br><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei;\">● </span></span>2000.09-2004.07</span>　<span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">清华大学工程物理系　获工程物理专业工学学士学位<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● </span>2011.09-至今<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">　</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"></span>清华大学工程物理系助理研究员、副研究员<br> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● </span>2009.09-2011.08<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">　</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"></span>清华大学物理系<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">　</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; border: 1px windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"></span>博士后</span></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● </span>本科课程：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">《工程应用中的物理奥妙与物理探索中的工程实践》（合讲）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● </span>研究生指导：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">指导（协助指导）已毕业博士生2人、硕士生5人，在读硕士生1人。</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">主要从事太赫兹光电子学领域的研究，重点涉及太赫兹探测物理与器件、太赫兹时域光谱分析技术、太赫兹成像理论与方法等方面的研究。</span></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">获得中国博士后科学基金（一等），主持国家自然科学基金项目2项，作为课题负责人或子课题负责人承担国家重点研发计划项目2项、国家重大科研仪器设备研制专项1项、国家科技支撑计划课题1项、横向项目3项，作为项目骨干参加国家自然科学基金联合基金重点项目2项、国家重大科学仪器设备开发专项1项等。</span></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">1. M. Chen, Y. Wang*, X. Wang, L. Li. Editorial: Advances in Terahertz Detection and Imaging. Frontiers in Physics, 10, 855623 (2022).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">2. M. Jin, Y. Wang, M. Chai, C. Chen, Z. Zhao*, T. He*. Terahertz Detectors Based on Carbon Nanomaterials. Advanced Functional Materials, 32, 2107499 (2022).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">3. M. Chai, Y. Wang, C. Chen, Z. Zhao*, M. Jin*, T. He*. Metamaterials‐Based Photoelectric Conversion: From Microwave to Optical Range. Laser &amp; Photonics Reviews, 16, 2100458 (2022).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">4. 吴炜东, 王迎新, 赵自然*. 太赫兹光热电探测方法研究进展. 科学通报, 67, 714 (2022).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">5. Y. Yu, L. Qiao, Y. Wang, Z. Zhao*. Active Millimeter Wave Three-Dimensional Scan Real-Time Imaging Mechanism with a Line Antenna Array. arXiv preprint arXiv:2102.04878 (2021).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">6. M. Chen, Y. Wang, Z. Zhao*. Localized Electromagnetic Resonance Enabled 