ly: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">26. Y. Wang*, Z. Zhao, Z. Chen, K. Kang. Calibration of a Thermal Detector for Pulse Energy Measurement of Terahertz Radiation. Optics Letters, 37, 4395 (2012).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">27. Y. Wang*, Z. Zhao, Z. Chen, L. Zhang, K. Kang, J. Deng. Continuous-Wave Terahertz Phase Imaging Using a Far-Infrared Laser Interferometer. Applied Optics, 50, 6452 (2011).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">28. Y. Wang*, Z. Zhao, Z. Chen, L. Zhang, K. Kang, J. Deng. Performance of the Continuous-Wave Imaging System Based on a Terahertz Gas Laser. Journal of Infrared and Millimeter Waves, 30, 193 (2011).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">29. Y. Wang, Z. Chen*, Z. Zhao, L. Zhang, K. Kang, Y. Zhang. Restoration of Terahertz Signals Distorted by Atmospheric Water Vapor Absorption. Journal of Applied Physics, 105, 103105 (2009).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">30. Y. Wang, Z. Zhao*, Z. Chen, L. Zhang, K. Kang. Diffraction-Induced Edge Contrast Enhancement for Terahertz Imaging. Chinese Optics Letters, 7, 690 (2009).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">31. Y. Wang, Z. Zhao*, Z. Chen, Y. Zhang, L. Zhang, K. Kang. Suppression of Spectral Interferences due to Water-Vapor Rotational Transitions in Terahertz Time-Domain Spectroscopy. Optics Letters, 33, 1354 (2008).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">32. Y. Wang, Z. Zhao, Z. Chen, K. Kang, B. Feng, Y. Zhang. Terahertz Absorbance Spectrum Fitting Method for Quantitative Detection of Concealed Contraband. Journal of Applied Physics, 102, 113108 (2007).</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 160%; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">●《Frontiers in Physics》期刊客座编辑</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● 美国光学学会（OSA）会员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● 担任若干国际著名期刊的审稿人，包括Nature、Applied Physics Letters、Optics Letters、Optics Express、Nanotechnology、Applied Optics、Optical Engineering等。</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● 2020年　北京市科学技术进步一等奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● 2014年　清华大学第十三届实验技术成果二等奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● 2013年　清华大学SRT计划优秀指导教师一等奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● 2010年　第三届国际光子与光电子学会议最佳论文奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">● 2009年　清华大学优秀博士学位论文二等奖</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"model-title\">\n                <div class=\"model\">常用链接</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"model-block\"></div>\n            <ul>\n      <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74493)\"><li>清华大学</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_ad